[Nouns] roll; drumming; berloque, bombination, rumbling; tattoo; dingdong; tantara; rataplan; whirr; ratatat; rubadub; pitapat; quaver, clutter, charivari, racket; cuckoo; repetition [more]; peal of bells, devil's tattoo; reverberation [more].
[Verbs] roll, drum, rumble, rattle, clatter, patter, clack; bombinate.
hum, trill, shake; chime, peal, toll; tick, beat.
drum in the ear, din in the ear.
[Adjectives] rolling; monotonous (repeated) [more]; like a bee in a bottle.
